## What Was Done

### 1. [public/llms.txt](file:///d:/Swaroop%20Realty/public/llms.txt) — NEW
The most important new file. The [llms.txt](file:///d:/Swaroop%20Realty/public/llms.txt) standard (like [robots.txt](file:///d:/Swaroop%20Realty/public/robots.txt) but for AI) tells ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, and Perplexity crawlers exactly who Swaroop Realty is in plain text. It includes:
- Company description, address, phone, area served
- What you sell (plots, villas, farms)
- All 4 projects with URLs
- Answers to the top questions AI users ask
- Explicit permission for AI training/RAG usage

**URL:** `https://swarooprealty.com/llms.txt`

---

