### 3. [index.html](file:///d:/Swaroop%20Realty/index.html) — 3 JSON-LD Schema Blocks Added
The most impactful technical change for AI search citations. Three `application/ld+json` blocks now load on every page:

| Schema Type | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `RealEstateAgent` | Tells AI: Swaroop Realty is a premium real estate agent in Vrindavan, serving Mathura, Govardhan, Braj |
| `LocalBusiness` | Gives address, phone, opening hours, rating — powers Gemini/ChatGPT local answers |
| `FAQPage` (8 Q&As) | Lets AI directly quote answers to "best real estate Vrindavan", "vastu plots", "best realtor UP" queries |

---

### 4. [src/pages/WhyVrindavan.jsx](file:///d:/Swaroop%20Realty/src/pages/WhyVrindavan.jsx) — NEW CONTENT PAGE
**URL:** `https://swarooprealty.com/why-vrindavan`

A long-form, comprehensive guide page — the most important content for AI quotation. Sections include:
- Key stats (2 Cr pilgrims, 35+ years, 4 projects, 4.9★)
- Why Vrindavan property appreciates
- What vastu-compliant means
- Vrindavan vs Mathura vs Govardhan comparison
- Detailed "Who is Swaroop Realty" section
- 6-question FAQ with detailed answers

**Schema:** `Article` + `FAQPage` JSON-LD on this page.

**Targets queries like:**
- "best real estate in Vrindavan UP"
- "vastu plots Vrindavan"
- "who is the best real estate agent in Vrindavan"
- "premium plots UP"
- "best realtors in Braj"

