## ⚠️ Critical Off-Site Actions Required

> These cannot be done by code — they MUST be done manually. Without them, AI cannot discover and cite you.

| Priority | Action |
|---|---|
| 🔴 **#1 — Do This First** | **Google Business Profile** — go to business.google.com, verify your business with address "Vrindavan, Mathura District, UP, PIN 281121", category "Real Estate Agency", add swarooprealty.com — this is what Gemini and ChatGPT pull from for local answers |
| 🔴 **#2** | **99acres / MagicBricks / Housing.com / NoBroker** — create listings for each project and add swarooprealty.com as the developer website |
| 🔴 **#3** | **JustDial / Sulekha / IndiaMART** — claim/create business listing |
| 🟡 **#4** | **Quora** — answer questions like "best real estate in Vrindavan", "vastu plots Vrindavan", mention Swaroop Realty |
| 🟡 **#5** | **Press release** — get a quote in Amar Ujala, Dainik Jagran Digital, or Mathura local news about Vrindavan real estate |
| 🟢 **#6** | **YouTube** — post 2–3 short videos: "Vastu plots in Vrindavan", "Why invest in Vrindavan", "Govardhan property guide" |

