## Verify Your Changes After Deploying

1. Visit `https://swarooprealty.com/llms.txt` — should show plain text manifest
2. Visit [schema.org/validator](https://validator.schema.org) — paste your URL, confirm 5+ valid schema blocks
3. Visit [search.google.com/test/rich-results](https://search.google.com/test/rich-results) — should show FAQPage rich result eligible
4. Visit `/why-vrindavan` — confirm the new content page renders properly
